{"tid":360940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch] Splatoon2 [16] 第一頁有Q&A同攻略 睇咗先問","createTime":"2017-08-15T16:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T17:04:14.000Z","uid":91718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29657c4dc25191918736a92f53247b78e80e124a","tid":360940,"uid":91718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_splatoon2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_splatoon2.png&h=19230c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Splatoon<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>  (スプラトゥーン<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>)</strong></span><br />\n遊戲/Amiibo/JoyCon/ProController 發售日期：2017-7-21<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg&h=c9c49d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg&h=dea22259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSplatoon是一款4對4 第三人稱射擊遊戲，與其他射擊遊戲有所不同<br />\n玩家需利用武器把地面塗色，佔色面積較多的一方獲勝<br />\n官方介紹片段(中文):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCROuiq-YjlI&d=kTTBxhKuG1eO8%2BXVsyK9QsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a81e820c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI</a><br />\n日本官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fswitch%2Faab6a&d=kTTBxhKuG1eO8%2BXVsyK9QsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f187a732\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a</a><br />\n日本官方Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter